short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: A plugin to get your LinkedIn profile to CVToBe

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Instead of typing everything again in CVToBe Resume Builder, download this extension. This extension will automatically import your LinkedIn profile data into CVToBe and build your resume that way. As with CVToBe, this extension too is completely free to download and use. We hope it makes your experience building a CV that much easier.
